Write a program to store their name and date_of_birth. The date_of_birth format should be dd/mm/yyyy. Write methods to read customer data as <name, dd/mm/yyyy> and display as <name, dd, mm, yyyy> using StringTokenizer class considering the delimiter character as “/”.

Sample Inputs	
Pusarla Venkata Sindhu
5/July/1995	

Sample Outputs
Pusarla Venkata Sindhu,5,July,1995


 //Please accept the inputs from the console and print the output
 #include <stdio.h>
 
 int main()
 {
    char name[100];
    char dob[20];
    
    gets(name);
    gets(dob);
    
    printf("%s,",name);
    for(int i=0;dob[i]!=NULL;i++){
        if(dob[i]=='/'){
            printf(",");
        }
        else
            printf("%c",dob[i]);
    }
    printf(",");
 return 0;
 }
 
